modules.description: Parses and generates XML-based property list data using a strict implementation of the Apple PropertyList DTD. It handles nested dictionaries, arrays, strings, integers, and binary data. Used to read and write configuration files and serialized data in macOS and iOS development workflows.

Provides functions to parse XML streams into Plist_xml.t structures, handling errors through exceptions and custom reporting. Operates on character streams and supports encoding, namespace, and entity resolution. Used to convert XML data from network sources into structured plist representations for processing.
